{
  "stem": "1581.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- at that time, my wife was highly pregnant and expected our baby, which was due on-- in this week that we were transported.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we received our pink slips, which was like a invitation to the transport.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother, my sister with her husband, my wife and I, we were bundled up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had to go into this school, where all people were collected to, to-- who had to be transported out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we had to leave our-- even the last place, although it was not what we used to be, but it was still our home.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were just uprooted completely.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And nobody knew what the future will bring.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to undergo our first taste of what life in-- without freedom will be, if you can call it freedom.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were collected in the school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All the windows were darkened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because the neighbors shouldn't see what was going on there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The sanitary conditions were terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was hardly any water, hardly any food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we-- it took them three days to strip us whatever valuables we still had and to process us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were allowed to have just a little suitcase.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And finally, in the night, we were marched to the train station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This march where, mind you, there were old people and there were little children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and there were beatings and there were shootings and there was-- it was quite a horrible let down and a horrible experience.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we finally were put into the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was a long, endless train ride, when we--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that-- we-- that was still a normal train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only in a compartment where there was supposed to be six people, there were 12 people.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
